Video4Linux.Net - a Mono interface to Video4Linux
Copyright (C) 2007-2008 Tim Taubert (twenty-three@users.berlios.de)
Licensed under the GPLv3.

Build
=====

Just type (as normal user):

	./configure
	make

Install
=======

If you want to install Video4Linux.Net, login as root user
and type:

	make install

Usage
=====

Be sure to reference "video4linux-net.dll" in your Mono code.
Then just use the library as described in the Tutorials or in
the Documentation.

Bugs
====

Please report any bugs under:

  http://developer.berlios.de/bugs/?group_id=8832

